summary: I had a dream that Taylor chose me for meeting, pointing me out, when she was flying above the crowd like during the Delicate at...
body: I had a dream that Taylor chose me for meeting, pointing me out, when she was flying above the crowd like during the Delicate at the concert and everything was RED… 🎶 🎸BUUURNING REEEEED!!🎸🎶 Literally. Then I walked somewhere and she suddenly showed up out of nowhere and was so kind and appreciative. We took some pictures although I really don’t like taking selfies in real life. The worst and the best of that was the feeling of constant happiness and certainty that everything will be okay. 💫
